Welcome to My City: Home. Drop by and visit your neighbors, Explore your house to find hidden treasures, check out the latest fashion and even make your own clothing at the fashion store! Everything is possible in My City. With lots of totally new characters, rooms, clothing and cool accessories every day is a new adventure where kids get to Play, Explore and Imagine.

Explore Your City Home
Explore your new home and visit your friendly neighbors. Can you find the two baby kittens hiding? Will you fix the leaking water pipe? Adventure and fun can be found everywhere in My City.

A New Story Every Day
Mom and Dad are away? It's a great opportunity to hold a party in the living room. Simply throw the pizza in the oven, turn on the disco ball and let the music play. With so many rooms and characters, we offer kids endless options for there very own pretend play game. 

Age Group 4-12 :
Easy enough for a 4 year old to play, Exciting enough for 10 years old to enjoy!

Key Game Features
- 12 locations including 2 apartments and a clothing store
- Tell your own story, create your own adventure, Each game is a new game play
- Lots of new characters, including 2 families with kids, babies and grownups of course.
- Free-Play stress free games, Extremely high play time 
- Customization of characters and rooms
- Daily gifts and prizes!
- Kids Safe and Ads Free.

Play Together
We support multi touch so kids can play together with friends and family on the same screen!

We love making children games, if you like what we do and want to send us ideas and suggestions for our next games of My City you can do so here:

description:
Jack Hartmann's original song, Make Straight and curved Lines, is an interactive video for pre-writing skills.
Practicing making Straight Lines will have students practicing straight lines vertically, horizontally and across.
Students will practice making slanted lines in both directions as they practice straight lines and get ready to write. Practicing straight lines, vertical lines and horizontal lines are prewriting strategies.
Practicing making Curved Lines will have students practicing curved lines as open and closed curves.
Students will practice making curved lines in both direction. as they practice curved lines and get ready to write. Practicing curved lines,both open and closed curves are prewriting strategies.

title: Floogals Learn Colors! Watch Floogals Games Online with colours for kids to learn Free Puzzle
tags: Floogals,floogals games online,floogals game,floogals learn colors,baby game,children games,games,kids games for boys,kids games for girls,video games,free,kids games,puzzle,adventure shows,childrenâ€™s adventure shows,game play,childrenâ€™s cartoons,preschoolers game,sprout,sprout tv,sprout floogals,preschool shows,sprout shows,colours for kids to learn,children,learn colors,toddlers,kids games to play for free,Fun Learning With Toys,FLWT
description:
Hi everyone!  This is Fun Learning With Toys Channel FLWT with a super special video of Floogals games online live gameplay!  In this video we're going to help the Floogals in a mission where we will learn colors with the Floogals!  In this mission we have to help the Floogals match the same colored bubbles with each other.  The more bubbles we get, the higher score we get!  After we complete the mission we get a new sticker.  It's a different sticker every time!

This is a really fun Floogals game and is a great representation of colours for kids to learn.  During the lesson I name the different colors that show up so children can retain the information through repetition.  The Floogals game is one of the great kids games to play for free.  It is available on the sprout TV website as a free service and is available for anyone to play.  When the Floogals learn colors, the kids will too, because this is one of the most engaging children games out there.  The music, the soundtrack features the iconic Floogals theme playing in the background while the but if you want something more befitting a game is going on.  It doesn't have the lyrics though, only an instrumental version.  This is a baby game that will not only help them learn colors but also their numbers because while finding the bubbles of various types, we count along from time to time.  

This game appeals to a wide audience.  This can be enjoyed as one of the kids games for girls. Floogals is definitely a Sprout show that appeals to both boys and girls.  There are three Floogals, Fleeker, Boomer, and Flo.  Flo is the second lieutenant of the cosmic crew and is the reasonable and level headed Floogal of the bunch. She helps Fleeker and Boomer when they make mistakes and  is always there to help save the day.  Girls will enjoy having a cool and fun character to look up to and always knows the right thing to do.  On the other hand, this is one of those very versatile video games.  It can be a great example of one of the kids games for boys.  Fleeker and Captain Boomer are two fun loving floogals who love to discover things and get into adventures.  Captain Fleeker is usually wrong about the things he investigates, and Flo Floogal sets the record straight and Fleeker usually takes the credit.  After the end of each sprout floogals episodes, all three floogals come together to make an important discovery.  They learn about whatever object they were trying to explore and learn a little more about what Humans are doing on earth. 

Floogals are one of those very well made preschool shows.  Each episode is set up from the perspective of a group of three toddlers and everyone gets to explore together.  It has all of the common tropes of an adventure show for kids.  They have fun, and interesting topics, a whole episode to focus on that eventually leads to a resolution that leaves everyone happy.  The Floogals game online tries to mimic the feeling of a children's adventure show.  Kids get to play along and learn their colors while one of their favorite Floogals characters looks on.  It's one of those kids games that that provide a fun and compelling puzzle for kids but isn't too difficult or too easy.  The game offer three difficulty settings: easy, medium, and hard.  During the game play, I play on the hard difficulty setting so viewers can see the game played in the most optimum level that I am capable off.  For it to be on the same level as any other adventure show, the game should be played on either on easy or medium mode.  There are not too many differences between the modes, except that there are bigger bubbles on the screen.  This allows players to group more bubbles together and makes it easier to get a larger score.

description:
Hi, welcome! Iron Man video game Disney Infinity 2.0 Marvel Super Heroes Spiderman playset. 2018 Best Avengers Iron Man superhero  video games and game movies,  and .

Iron Man is a 2008 American superhero film based on the Marvel Comics character of the same name, produced by Marvel Studios and distributed by Paramount Pictures.

Genius, billionaire, and playboy Tony Stark, who has inherited the defense contractor Stark Industries from his father, is in war-torn Afghanistan with his friend and military liaison Lieutenant Colonel James Rhodes to demonstrate the new "Jericho" missile. After the demonstration, the convoy is ambushed and Stark is critically wounded by one of his own company's rocket-propelled grenades. He is captured and imprisoned in a cave by a terrorist group, the Ten Rings; Yinsen, a fellow captive who is a doctor, implants an electromagnet into Stark's chest to keep the shrapnel shards that wounded him from reaching his heart and killing him. Ten Rings leader Raza offers Stark freedom in exchange for building a Jericho missile for the group, but Tony and Yinsen know that Raza will not keep his word.

Disney Infinity 3.0 features similar gameplay mechanics to Disney Infinity and Disney Infinity: Marvel Super Heroes. Although sharing many key elements, the game's combat system has been redesigned to become more in-depth and complex.

A play set featuring Marvel characters fighting each other on a series of levels. The story sees Loki working together with Ultron to manipulate all of the universe's heroes into fighting each other using robot duplicates while they steal one of the six Infinity Stones from the Asgardian vault. All Marvel characters from Disney Infinity 2.0 are playable in this playset, along with new characters introduced in 3.0, such as Hulkbuster, Ant-Man, Black Panther, Vision and Ultron. This is also the first play set to utilize four-player local gameplay.

tags: PBS Kids (TV Network),Public Broadcasting Service (TV Network),kart kingdom
description:
Customize your own kart, create your own adventure, and explore new worlds in Kart Kingdom â€“ a new free game just for kids by PBS KIDS.

Play Kart Kingdom at http://to.pbs.org/kidskartkingdom

Kart Kingdom is based on the system thinking curriculum. Any curriculum and educational resources for Kart Kingdom is developed with the help of our educational advisor, Arizona State Universityâ€™s Center for Games and Impact.

Kart Kingdom helps players understand systems. A system refers to several different things that work together to create a whole, such as the pipes in the water system. Without the pipes, water cannot travel from the dam to your faucet at home. The idea of systems thinking is for an individual to understand what the system is and how it works. To be able to process using systems thinking is a crucial life skill for scientists, engineers, etc.

description:
Untitled Goose Game is out now!
It's a lovely morning in the village and you are a horrible goose.

description:
Hi, welcome! Disney Pixar Cars playset - Video game Disney Infinity 1.0 with Lightning McQueen, Mater, Holley Shiftwell and Francesco Bernoulli from the movie. 2018 Best  video games and race cars game movies, ,  and .

Disney Infinity was an action-adventure sandbox video game developed by Avalanche Software and published by Disney Interactive Studios. Disney Infinity is an action-adventure game with physical toys, open world creation, and story-driven game-play. Characters, playsets, and other features are brought into the game using figurines and discs with the included Infinity Base.

Cars is a 2006 American computer-animated comedy-adventure film produced by Pixar Animation Studios and released by Walt Disney Pictures.

In a world populated by anthropomorphic vehicles, the last race of the Piston Cup championship ends in a three-way tie between retiring veteran Strip "The King" Weathers, infamous runner-up Chick Hicks, and rookie Lightning McQueen. The tiebreaker race is scheduled for one week later at the Los Angeles International Speedway in California. Lightning is desperate to win the race, since it would not only make him the first rookie to win a championship, but also allow him to leave the unglamorous sponsorship of Rust-eze and allow him to take The King's place as the sponsored car of the lucrative Dinoco team. Eager to start practice in California as soon as possible, he pushes his big rig, Mack, to travel all night long. While McQueen is sleeping, the exhausted Mack drifts off and is startled by a gang of four reckless street racers, causing McQueen to fall out the back of the trailer and onto the road. McQueen wakes in the middle of traffic and speeds off the highway to find Mack, only to end up in the run-down desert town of Radiator Springs, while inadvertently ruining the pavement of its main road.

title: LOKI Cartoon Game Videos for Kids - Marvel Video Games for Children - Disney Infinity
tags: loki,loki cartoon,loki games,loki videos,avengers,avengers cartoon,avengers for kids,avenger cartoon,games,avengers kids,cartoon,avengers kids cartoon,kids videos for kids,superhero kids,superheroes,game videos,games for kids,cartoons for kids,superhero cartoon,marvel cartoons,avengers cartoons,cartoon games,videos for kids,marvel superheroes,video games for children,disney infinity 2.0,kids videos,kids games,game videos for kids
description:
Hi, welcome! Marvel Villain Loki with the Avengers in the video game Disney Infinity 2.0 Marvel Super Heroes playset. 2018 Best superhero  video games and game movies,  and .

Disney Infinity was an action-adventure sandbox video game developed by Avalanche Software and published by Disney Interactive Studios. Disney Infinity is an action-adventure game with physical toys, open world creation, and story-driven game-play. Characters, playsets, and other features are brought into the game using figurines and discs with the included Infinity Base.

Disney Infinity: Marvel Super Heroes (also known as Disney Infinity 2.0 Edition) is an action-adventure sandbox toys-to-life[6] video game developed by Avalanche Software and published by Disney Interactive Studios. The game features additional work by Studio Gobo and Ninja Theory. It is the sequel and successor of the 2013 video game Disney Infinity and was announced on April 8, 2014. 

Featuring original story material by Brian Michael Bendis, Marvel Super Heroes includes multiple plots and includes characters from both Marvel and Disney properties. The main campaign is divided into three stories. The first storyline follows the Avengers as they prevent the Norse God Loki from rebuilding the Casket of Ancient Winters. The second storyline centers on Spider-Man and features him and his team tasked with the objective to stop Green Goblin's symbiote invasion. The third and final storyline concentrates around the Guardians of the Galaxy, in a plot heavily inspired by the Guardians of the Galaxy film, where the Guardians must protect Knowhere from Ronan the Accuser.

Disney Infinity: Marvel Super Heroes expands Disney Infinity's array of tools to use in the Toybox mode, an open world sandbox. Additionally, the ability to personalize individual characters has been added, using a Skill Tree. Marvel Super Heroes adds on the previous game's community sharing options, including the sharing of personal creations.

It was also the first Marvel-licensed game to be published by Disney Interactive Studios, due to Sega's contract with Marvel expiring after the release of Captain America: Super Soldier in 2011, and Activision's contract expiring after the release of The Amazing Spider-Man 2, released a few months prior to the release of the game. A sequel, Disney Infinity 3.0, was released on August 28, 2015 in Europe and August 29, 2015 in North America.

Meet Peppa Pig and her family:

Peppa Pig
Peppa Pig is a lovable but slightly bossy little pig. She is four years old and lives with Mummy Pig, Daddy Pig and her little brother George. Peppa likes playing with her best friend Suzy Sheep, visiting Granny and Grandpa Pig and looking after George. Most of all, Peppa loves jumping up and down in muddy puddles, laughing and making loud snorting noises.

George Pig
George is Peppaâ€™s little brother. He is 18 months old and loves to play with his big sister, Peppa â€“ even when sheâ€™s being bossy. Georgeâ€™s favourite thing is his toy dinosaur. He carries it everywhere with him. George canâ€™t speak yet but can say one word very well: â€˜Dine-saw!â€™

Mummy Pig
Mummy Pig likes jumping up and down in muddy puddles almost as much as Peppa. She works from home on her computer and sometimes lets Peppa and George help, as long as they donâ€™t bash the keyboard. She is better at map reading than Daddy Pig and is very wise about most things.

Daddy Pig
Daddy Pig is very jolly and laughs all the time, especially when he plays with Peppa and George. Daddy Pig reads the paper and gets excited about trips in the car. He loves cookies and pumpkin pie and Peppa teases him about his big round tummy. Daddy Pig can be a tiny bit grumpy sometimes when he canâ€™t remember where he put his glasses.

What is Roblox? Roblox is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. Itâ€™s unique in that practically everything on Roblox is designed and constructed by members of the community. Roblox is designed for 8 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore Roblox â€” interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything â€” be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer â€œCapture the Flagâ€ game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, Roblox members can earn specialty badges as well as Roblox dollars (â€œRobuxâ€). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.
